input.content: What day of the week does the following sentence mean? Answer only with the first three letters of the day of the week. The answer must be one of 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat', or 'Sun' with no explanation

example.output: t.union(t.literal('Mon'), t.literal('Tue'), t.literal('Wed'), t.literal('Thu'), t.literal('Fri'), t.literal('Sat'), t.literal('Sun'))
